race.comment: FLYING FRANKIE (1) hasn't been beaten far in stronger races than this so far this campaign, finishing 1.2L away when favourite behind a smart one last time out. The inside draw is a big tick and if he can run up to his recent form up in weight, then he'll give them something to chase. SPICY THANG (2) was ridden quieter last start at Belmont and stormed home to win by 0.3L over this trip. Suspect they'll do the same from a wide barrier today. The figures she turned in last start are strong for a race like this and while she rises in weight, she can bring up back-to-back wins. NINETYMILESTRAIGHT (7) just missed fresh before finishing 2.6L behind what looks a good one last time out. Maps to get every chance once again and can put herself in the finish. WILUNA LASS (8) disappointed on debut but has been back tot he trials since where she was impressive. Can bounce back in a big way. BAMBINO CHINO (6) bolted in at the trials recently and has to be included.
